Title: Chase your dream before it&#39;s too late
DateModified: '2019-03-05'
DatePublished: '2019-03-05'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/chase-your-dream-before-it-s-too-late
SetInCountry: Brazil
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Andre Issa
AuthorCountry: Brazil
Text: Every single day, when I came back home from work, I kept thinking about how
  my life could be different if I had done that trip. Once I lost my fear to do so,
  I bought the passage and went. Went to a different world, knew new people and new
  cultures, it was a leap into the unknown.
